R Resource efficiency

Progress on DEGREE ambition #6: Next-level Robust Eco Design for 100% of relevant Siemens product families by 2030

The quota of Robust Eco Design implementation for the relevant portfolio elements currently stands at 51% compared to 35% in the year 2022. Only when the rate of implementation reaches 100% can it be assumed that all relevant product families have com- pleted each individual phase for Robust Eco Design.

Progress  FY 21: 26%  51%  100% by 2030  Siemens without SHS 